OL,3,CRugby clubs trigger EGM with WRU over
OL,4,C'chaos created by current leadership'
OL,6,FLocal rugby clubs in Wales have
OL,7,Fwritten to the Welsh Rugby Union
OL,8,Fcalling for an Extraordinary General
OL,9,FMeeting (EGM) which if given the go
OL,10,Fahead, would see a vote of no
OL,11,Fconfidence held in the Chair, Richard
OL,12,FCollier-Keywood.
OL,14,FIt comes following ongoing controversy
OL,15,Faround attempts of the WRU to reduce
OL,16,Fthe number of clubs in Wales from four
OL,17,Fto three, which could see the end of
OL,18,FSwansea based side the Ospreys.
