OL,3,CRugby clubs trigger EGM with WRU over
OL,4,C'chaos created by current leadership'
OL,6,FSwansea West MP Torsten Bell is urging
OL,7,Fall clubs to attend the meeting saying
OL,8,Fit's a chance to "bring an end to the
OL,9,Fchaos created by the current WRU
OL,10,Fleadership."
OL,12,F"The WRU are trying to shrink Welsh
OL,13,Frugby and end professional rugby in
OL,14,FWales's second city. If this isn't an
OL,15,Femergency, I don't know what is.
OL,17,F"So it's totally right that so many
OL,18,Fclubs have come together to call this
OL,19,FEmergency General Meeting. They are
OL,20,Fbravely standing up for Welsh rugby
OL,21,Fand all our communities
