OL,3,CRugby clubs trigger EGM with WRU over
OL,4,C'chaos created by current leadership'
OL,6,F"For weeks supporters, players and
OL,7,Fcommunities have been asking the WRU
OL,8,Fto put a stop to their chaotic plans.
OL,9,FBut there are no signs they are
OL,10,Flistening.
OL,12,F"Grassroot clubs have now concluded
OL,13,Fthat the only way to ensure the WRU
OL,14,Fchanges course is to change the
OL,15,Fleadership. I agree.
OL,17,F"I urge all clubs to attend the EGM,
OL,18,Fvote for a change of leadership and
OL,19,Fbring this chaos to an end."
