OL,3,CRugby clubs trigger EGM with WRU over
OL,4,C'chaos created by current leadership'
OL,6,FIt recently emerged that Y11 - the
OL,7,Fcurrent owner of the Ospreys - have
OL,8,Fexpressed their interest to the WRU to
OL,9,Fpurchase Cardiff Rugby, a decision
OL,10,Fwhich has not gone down well with
OL,11,Fsupporters, former players, and
OL,12,Fpoliticians.
OL,14,FWhat happens now?
OL,16,FThe WRU has acknowledged the news of a
OL,17,Frequest for an EGM, saying it will
OL,18,Frespond in 21 days, giving it time to
OL,19,Fassess if the request is compliant
OL,20,Fwith its Constitution to pave the way
OL,21,Ffor an EGM.
