OL,3,CRugby clubs trigger EGM with WRU over
OL,4,C'chaos created by current leadership'
OL,6,FIt adds that once notice is given the
OL,7,FEGM must be held within 28 days.
OL,9,FThe WRU made public its plan to change
OL,10,Fthe amount of clubs from four to three
OL,11,Fin October 2025 following an extensive
OL,12,Fconsultation to try and find a way of
OL,13,Fimproving the state of the game.
OL,15,FIn a statement following calls for an
OL,16,FEGM it says "we are now focused on
OL,17,Frolling out that plan and have been
OL,18,Fworking tirelessly with the key
OL,19,Fstakeholders during the last months to
OL,20,Fagree a consensus on its
OL,21,Fimplementation.
