OL,3,CRugby clubs trigger EGM with WRU over
OL,4,C'chaos created by current leadership'
OL,6,F"This detailed work has been
OL,7,Fundertaken with the professional
OL,8,Fclubs, the United Rugby Championship
OL,9,Fand playerJrepresentatives, and we
OL,10,Fremain committed to reaching consensus
OL,11,Fon the next steps.
OL,13,F"We ask all stakeholders to continue
OL,14,Fworking with us. We recognise that
OL,15,Fchange is challenging, but it is
OL,16,Fessential for the long-term health of
OL,17,Fthe game in Wales."
