OL,3,CRugby clubs trigger EGM with WRU over
OL,4,C'chaos created by current leadership'
OL,6,FIf the EGM is given the green light by
OL,7,Fthe WRU it could have ramifications
OL,8,Fthat are potentially seismic on the
OL,9,Fgame here in Wales.
OL,11,FIf Richard Collier-Keywood and Malcolm
OL,12,FWall were to lose a vote of no
OL,13,Fconfidence resulting from the EGM it
OL,14,Fcould potential derail the WRU's plans
OL,15,Fto restructure professional rugby.
OL,17,FBut if they won it, it could mean that
OL,18,Fthey have a mandate to progress
OL,19,Fforward with their plans and change
OL,20,Fthe game in Wales as we currently know
OL,21,Fit.
